Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.70,0:00:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能接下我的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.97,0:00:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.13,0:00:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七顆星！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.37,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七顆！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.87,0:00:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貨物…這孩子就麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.68,0:00:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艇駕駛克勞士‧沃卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.71,0:00:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此接下\N拉爾夫‧溫斯地神聖的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.15,0:00:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.02,0:00:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你一定要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.76,0:00:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.60,0:00:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.71,0:00:54.70,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.78,0:00:57.25,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.85,0:01:04.09,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說把黎明　當作是一個開始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.03,0:01:12.02,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說現在就是來臨的時刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.10,0:01:16.93,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的煙雲時代交響曲 飛向雲海的彼端 \N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony  雲の海の向こうに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.00,0:01:23.14,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飛往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.58,0:01:40.82,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那一刻？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.89,0:01:55.37,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.44,0:02:04.84,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個像星星的東西\N真的跟拉爾夫所說的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.51,0:02:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會對引擎的音紋有反應的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.74,0:02:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不能走空中路線了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開水路後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越過瀑布就是尼布羅森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要穿越那裡，就到神殿前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.82,0:02:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.02,0:02:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.63,0:02:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫做行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.19,0:02:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，我把行經路線定好了\N請妳待會兒確認一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.93,0:02:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要我說幾次啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.83,0:02:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你放棄這個工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經想好了安全路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題就剩下燃料了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.01,0:03:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你有沒有在聽我說話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七顆星耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.44,0:03:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有看過這樣的工作嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.31,0:03:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很有魄力不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這當中絕對另有隱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.69,0:03:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不然也不會標七顆星說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.06,0:03:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以做得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.39,0:03:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你憑什麼那麼有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.16,0:03:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是放那裡，拿到這邊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.20,0:03:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉爾夫他是相信我們\N才會把工作托付給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就盡全力去做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.01,0:03:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位拉爾夫也已經掛了好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}緊急狀況\NZugzwang
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.30,0:04:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追兵或許已經到了附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.73,0:04:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.67,0:04:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它已經被捲入那場爆炸裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你確定嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的情況下不可能沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.41,0:04:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.51,0:04:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去檢查一下引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.58,0:04:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是走水路過來的\N得讓引擎轉一陣才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.69,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.55,0:04:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不把水排掉的話\N明天可飛不起來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.26,0:04:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再等一段時間好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.68,0:04:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對這次工作最不爽的一點\N就是交貨對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.48,0:04:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是說銀之戰艦嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.32,0:04:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去送貨給那艘船試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真以為你還能活著回來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是聽說過有一些傳言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.32,0:05:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦為了補給燃料\N曾經降落在瑪雅薩村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.56,0:05:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是兩年前的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.73,0:05:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是村子裡見過那艘船的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今已經一個都不剩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.67,0:05:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.80,0:05:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家都死光了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.84,0:05:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說最後一個人\N整整纏綿病榻了一年半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.51,0:05:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後滿身皺紋的死掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.88,0:05:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一開始也是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.58,0:05:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，最後死掉的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說就是胖胖雞她外婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說胖胖雞她…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.59,0:05:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事大家都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.53,0:05:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說在她脖子上\N還出現了奇怪的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳說的是雞婆婆的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.67,0:05:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三天前我在市場碰到她的時候\N她還叫我比賽時要加油呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.20,0:05:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說\N反正我還不想死啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.58,0:05:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳起來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.62,0:06:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.36,0:06:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.26,0:06:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…妳還在睡的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經完成工作的交接了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.03,0:06:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.47,0:06:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔…姬塔她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.20,0:06:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那位和妳同機的人是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她先回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.14,0:06:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說還有很多工作要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.45,0:06:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吃看嘛，很好吃唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還會回來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.03,0:06:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是問…姬塔嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.21,0:06:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一個人就什麼事都不會做嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.02,0:07:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是姬塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.72,0:07:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒，不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一等啊，艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.60,0:07:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔，姬塔，姬塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.80,0:07:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.62,0:07:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔她今天不會來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.59,0:07:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我們三個人\N要一起去見她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等明早起床後，就一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.17,0:07:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.51,0:08:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把水都排掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟妳說別發動引擎的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.18,0:08:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果連飛都飛不起來\N還能幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.73,0:08:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我和拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒她睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.55,0:09:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小的孩子\N為什麼要用七顆星來運送呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.52,0:09:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你還是別多想的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.59,0:10:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好不要介入太深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒她也是孤零零一個人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.91,0:12:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.10,0:12:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒，跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.90,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.73,0:12:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.77,0:12:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.31,0:13:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水，水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個絕不能丟下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.26,0:13:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房子毀了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都可以從天花板看見天空了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧，艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.80,0:13:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是這樣，它又追過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直追，一直追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，快發動引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.11,0:13:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會被幹掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.63,0:14:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不曉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.55,0:14:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙會對引擎產生反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.51,0:14:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算一直往前走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.68,0:14:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方向沒錯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.59,0:14:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一個岔路是最後的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往右邊會經過先鋒艇組織總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.43,0:14:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是交給他們吧，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.91,0:14:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，走右邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.51,0:14:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.38,0:14:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我還是打算要把這個工作完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.72,0:14:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完了\N我短暫的人生就此結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.33,0:15:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.93,0:15:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總會有辦法的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.07,0:15:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從礦山流下來的克勞地亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣沈積在水道中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.30,0:15:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.34,0:15:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.48,0:15:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過偷偷撿走的話\N是會被抓起來的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒事了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，這給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.60,0:16:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐剩下的\N不過一個人只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.17,0:16:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇她只有吃的東西\N是絕不會忘了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.98,0:16:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛有說什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊，那我要吃囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.92,0:16:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.79,0:16:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒她說好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一個轉角右轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.86,0:16:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.87,0:16:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒她在哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.91,0:17:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔她…\N其實已經不在了對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.02,0:17:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.51,0:17:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.68,0:17:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一點點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.25,0:17:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿過前面的森林\N就到目的地的神殿遺跡了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.96,0:17:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.62,0:17:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，出口還在更前面才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.49,0:17:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，快發動引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.27,0:18:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.24,0:18:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.68,0:18:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好抓緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.32,0:18:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用力吸一口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.65,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，住手呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.02,0:18:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屏住呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然把這種東西帶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次是真的出口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.32,0:18:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是瀑布哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.32,0:18:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好鉤繩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.41,0:19:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.97,0:19:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.91,0:19:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.86,0:19:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再撐著點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.74,0:19:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.37,0:19:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活該
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.37,0:20:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.71,0:20:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇妳也沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命去了半條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.12,0:20:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神殿…遺跡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.93,0:20:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接妳的人應該馬上就會到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.11,0:20:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要保重哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.85,0:20:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.72,0:20:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.19,0:21:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.20,0:21:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.57,0:21:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.64,0:21:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把艾兒放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.25,0:21:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.95,0:21:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.32,0:22:40.25,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.29,0:22:47.16,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く  でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.23,0:22:52.46,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.53,0:22:58.30,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.37,0:23:03.97,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你捨命奮鬥的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.04,0:23:12.51,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我不禁啞口無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.19,0:23:18.49,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.56,0:23:24.52,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.60,0:23:30.66,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無論風有多麼強\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.74,0:23:36.44,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會折斷的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.51,0:23:47.35,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我會擁有那樣一對翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.56,0:23:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（下回預告）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.16,0:23:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算完成了與拉爾夫的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.79,0:23:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.56,0:23:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害耶，有七顆星耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.50,0:23:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保證會把先鋒艇組織的\N那些老先生們給嚇壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.73,0:24:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大肥雞搞不好還會因為\N震驚過度而飛上天呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.37,0:24:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一個人在銀之戰艦上\N會不會感覺害怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.70,0:24:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒她才不是貨物呢\N妳說對不對，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.48,0:24:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最後流亡 第五話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.68,0:24:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步步逼近\NPositional play
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.28,0:24:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下我短暫的人生\N可真的要結束了
